フの1日の流れ</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__time\">8:30</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item-content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__tit\">出社</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__txt\">今日配達する牛乳やヨーグルトを自分の車に積みこみます。</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../img/recruit/img_job01_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__img\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__time\">9:00</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item-content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__tit\">出発　配送開始</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__txt\">宅配ボックスが約8割、手渡しが約2割です。自分のペースで配達します。</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../img/recruit/img_job01_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__img\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__time\">12:00</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item-content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__tit\">昼休憩</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__txt\">好きな時間に休憩可能です。</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../img/recruit/img_job01_d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__img\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item__time\">13:00</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jobContent-schedule-list__item-content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t